Interface ExtendCoordAxis

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExtendTimeCoordAxis
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ExtendCoordAxis
    Interface for classes implementing Extended axis metadata: not only x,y,z,time.
